name: Literal value truncated at runtime
priority: MINOR
tags: pitfall,confusing
type: CODE_SMELL
description:
The value of this literal is truncated at runtime. This will raise unexpected results.

## Non compliant

```natural
DEFINE DATA LOCAL
1 #VAR (A1)
END-DEFINE

#VAR := 'Hi'
WRITE #VAR
END
```

## Compliant

```natural
DEFINE DATA LOCAL
1 #VAR (A1)
END-DEFINE

#VAR := 'H'
WRITE #VAR
END
```
